# Cursor Rules — @dangbt/pro-ui Project

## UI Component Library
This project uses **@dangbt/pro-ui**. Always use pro-ui components instead of building from scratch.

## Import Rule
```tsx
// Always import from the package root
import { Button, ProTable, Modal, Badge } from '@dangbt/pro-ui'
```

## Component Selection Guide

| Need | Use |
|------|-----|
| Data table with pagination | `ProTable` with `request` prop (server) or `dataSource` prop (client) |
| Form with validation | `ProForm` + `ProFormInput/Select/DatePicker` etc. |
| App shell / sidebar nav | `Layout` component |
| Modal / dialog | `Modal` inside `DialogTrigger` from react-aria-components |
| Side panel / filter | `Drawer` inside `DialogTrigger` |
| Floating menu | `Menu` inside `DialogTrigger` |
| Toast notification | `toast.success()` / `toast.error()` (mount `<ToastProvider />` once at root) |
| Inline alert | `Alert` with variant prop |
| KPI metric | `Statistic` with trend prop |
| Status label | `Badge` with variant: success/warning/danger/info |
| Loading state | `Spinner` or `Skeleton` |
| Empty state | `Empty` with title, description, action |
| Multi-step UI | `Steps` |
| Tab navigation | `Tabs` + `TabList` + `TabPanel` |
| User avatar | `Avatar` (initials fallback) or `AvatarGroup` |
| Dark/light toggle | `useTheme()` from ThemeProvider |

## Button Rules
- Use `onPress` not `onClick`
- Variants: `solid` (primary action), `outline` (secondary), `ghost` (tertiary), `danger` (destructive)
- Always set `type="submit"` on form submit buttons

## Color / Theming Rules
- Use semantic tokens NOT hardcoded Tailwind colors for theme-sensitive UI:
  - ✅ `bg-surface`, `bg-surface-subtle`, `bg-canvas`, `text-fg`, `text-fg-muted`, `border-border`
  - ❌ `bg-white`, `bg-gray-100`, `text-gray-900` (breaks dark mode)
- Primary brand color: `text-primary`, `bg-primary`

## ProTable Column Types
valueType options: `'text'` | `'number'` | `'date'` | `'dateRange'` | `'select'` | `'money'` | `'custom'`

## Required App Setup
```tsx
// Must be in App root:
<ThemeProvider defaultTheme="system">
  <ToastProvider />
  {/* app content */}
</ThemeProvider>
```

## MCP Server (optional, for AI assistance)
```bash
# Add to get live component API access in Cursor
# Add to .cursor/mcp.json:
# { "mcpServers": { "pro-ui": { "command": "npx", "args": ["-y", "mcp-pro-ui"] } } }
```
